Class RegisterUserActivityTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301f20t14.bookbox.RegisterUserActivityTest

  • public class RegisterUserActivityTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Test class for RegisterUserActivity. All UI tests related to RegisterUserActivity are written. Robotium test framework is used. ** Make sure that no user is logged in before starting the tests Users are signed out after each test (@Before is not early enough) so try running the test twice
    Version:
    2020.11.15
    Author:
    Olivier Vadiavaloo, Carter Sabadash
